headline: Electronic Arts Is Going Private. Is It Too Late to Buy EA Stock?
summary: Saudi Arabia's PIF is buying the company for $55 billion, but some analysts are not convinced that the deal will succeed.

headline: New $17 Million Bet on STAAR Surgical Comes as Sales Jump 7% and Margins Hit 82%
